## Findings

### ✅ What's Working Well
- **Full CRUD API coverage**: 57+ API functions covering all entities
- **Auto-assign system**: AI-powered candidate-job matching with scores
- **CV Manager**: Review modal with overview, remarks, applications, and allocate tabs
- **Project structure**: Jobs belong to projects, projects have team assignments
- **Communication channels**: WhatsApp, SMS, email, in-person tracking

### ⚠️ Issues Found

#### 1. Dashboard Needs Robust Visualizations (User Reported: "Dashboard looks boring")
- **Current**: Basic stat cards (candidates, jobs, applications, projects) + recent activity list + upcoming interviews
- **Missing**: Charts, trend lines, pipeline funnels, geographic distribution, time-series data
- **Fix**: Add chart library (Recharts), implement pipeline funnel, source distribution pie chart, hiring trend line chart, geographic heatmap, conversion rate metrics

#### 2. UI/UX Makeover Needed (User Reported: "Shades of blue as primary")
- **Current theme**: Indigo/purple primary (`#6366f1` = primary-500), not blue
- **Fix**: Switch to blue palette (e.g., `#3b82f6` blue-500 family), add modern glassmorphism effects, improve card designs, add micro-animations

#### 3. CV View/Download/AI Insights
- **Current**: [CVManager.jsx](file:///d:/Dewan%20Project/recruitment-system/frontend/src/pages/CVManager.jsx) has review modal with overview tabs
- **Issues to verify**:
  - CV file viewing (PDF preview in modal?)
  - CV download functionality
  - AI insights display (match scores, suitability analysis)
- **Fix**: Ensure CV preview iframe/viewer works, add explicit download button, enhance AI insights panel with percentage & reasoning

#### 4. Agent Assignment — Suitability Suggestions Missing
- **User requirement**: "Show the agent who assigns the candidate what other jobs the candidate would be suitable for with percentage and reasonings"
- **Current**: [JobCandidates.jsx](file:///d:/Dewan%20Project/recruitment-system/frontend/src/pages/JobCandidates.jsx) has match scores but may not show alternative job suggestions
- **Fix**: Add "Other Suitable Jobs" panel when assigning a candidate, showing match % and reasoning

#### 5. Critical Mismatch Highlighting
- **User requirement**: "If the job requirement parameters are less or not matching show critically"
- **Current**: Auto-assign has scoring but may not visually highlight critical mismatches
- **Fix**: Add red/amber visual indicators for critical mismatches in the candidate review view

#### 6. Loading & System Animations (User Reported)
- **Current**: Basic skeleton loaders exist ([Skeleton.jsx](file:///d:/Dewan%20Project/recruitment-system/frontend/src/components/ui/Skeleton.jsx))
- **Missing**: Page transition animations, loading spinners, button click animations, toast animations, table row enter animations
- **Fix**: Add framer-motion for page transitions, pulsing loaders, stagger animations on lists

